.worksheet-wp
  .title-text
    h2 Get Your Free "Design Your Ideal Life" Workbook
    h3 Get all 12 infographic worksheets and start planning your own Ideal Me Challenge today!
  .offer-section
    .container
      .worksheet-column
        .worksheet
          = image_tag "wksht01.png", width: 160
          h4 Vision Board
          p
            | A place where you can create your Ideal Me vision using stickers, pictures, quotes and cut-outs that represent your ideal self
        .worksheet
          = image_tag "wksht02.png", width: 160
          h4 Life Balance Worksheet
          p
            | Evaluate your commitments and refocus your time on the areas that matter most to you
        .worksheet
          = image_tag "wksht03.png", width: 160
          h4 What Makes Me Happy?
          p
            | Remember the people, places and things that bring joy to your life and experience them more often
        .worksheet
          = image_tag "wksht04.png", width: 160
          h4 If I Could…
          p
            | There are no limits – let yourself imagine the goals you wish to accomplish and plan to realize them sooner rather than later
        .worksheet
          = image_tag "wksht05.png", width: 160
          h4 I Want, I Need
          p
            | Helping you realize what it is you truly want and need to better design your ideal life
        .worksheet
          = image_tag "wksht06.png", width: 160
          h4 Words to Live By
          p
            | A place to store quotes that speak to you for long term inspiration that will keep you on track to reaching your ideal self
      .worksheet-column
        .worksheet
          = image_tag "wksht08.png", width: 160
          h4 Ideal Me To-Do List
          p
            | A simple to-do list that will free up mental space and allow you to remain focus on your progress rather than day-to-day tasks
        .worksheet
          = image_tag "your-values.jpg", width: 160
          h4 What Do I Value?
          p
            | Identify what truly matters to you so you can focus on goals that bring you the most satisfaction
        .worksheet
          = image_tag "wksht09.png", width: 160
          h4 Top 3 Ideal Me Goals
          p
            | Identify your next steps through the use of highly effective Ideal Me reverse engineering strategies and life hacks
        .worksheet
          = image_tag "wksht10.png", width: 160
          h4 Gamify Your Life
          p
            | Stay inspired to achieve success and allow yourself to indulge on guilty pleasures… because you’ve earned them!
        .worksheet
          = image_tag "wksht11.png", width: 160
          h4 Ideal Me Career Plan
          p
            | A dynamic way of defining and creating a clear, direct pathway to your dream career
        .worksheet
          = image_tag "wksht12.png", width: 160
          h4 My Ideal Day
          p
            | Discover how to transform your current day into your ideal day through the power of reverse engineering
      .clear
.courses-wp
  .title-text
    h2 Courses That Really Work
    h3 The 1st 100% satisfaction guaranteed community of curated products that get results or your money back!
  p.top-text
    | All courses backed by the
    a href="/static/about"
      |  Ideal Me Seal.
    |  If you're not satisfied you get a full refund.

  .offer-section
    .container
      - i = 0
      - @courses.each do |course|
        = render partial: 'partials/course_card', locals: {course: course}
        - i = i + 1
        - if i % 4 == 0
          .clear
      .clear
